        <updateDate>2021-11-16T16:12:34Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Colonel John McHugh Tuition Fairness for Survivors Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to disapprove courses of education provided by public institutions of higher learning if such institutions charge a higher rate for tuition and fees than in-state tuition for individuals who are entitled to educational assistance under the Survivors' and Dependents' Educational Assistance program.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
